snippet.title: Sonic Tameshi - SAGE 2024 Demo Trailer
snippet.description:
Hey! Sonic Tameshi is my new project, a Sonic Fan Game based on Sonic CD,
This demo contains the first zone " Radiant Roots ".

Download the DEMO:
https://sonicfangameshq.com/forums/showcase/sonic-tameshi-sage-2024-demo.2193/

Check out the soundtrack!:

RR Act 1: https://on.soundcloud.com/h2Nk2ns7BM7JS4Kf9

RR Act 2: https://on.soundcloud.com/dHP7eEk6mHSosCit5
